name: html5shiv
description: the html5 shiv enables use of html5 sectioning elements in legacy internet explorer and provides basic html5 styling for internet explorer 6-9, safari 4.x (and iphone 3.x), and firefox 3.x.
kwds: the html5 shiv enables use of html5 sectioning elements in legacy internet explorer and provides basic html5 styling for internet explorer 6-9, safari 4.x (and iphone 3.x), and firefox 3.x.
